  <sect2 role="installation">
    <title>Installation de Kde-runtime</title>

    <para>Installez <application>kderuntime</application> en lançant les commandes
    suivantes&nbsp;:</para>

<screen><userinput>patch -Np1 -i ../kde-runtime-&kderuntime-version;-rpc_fix-1.patch &amp;&amp;
mkdir build &amp;&amp;
cd build &amp;&amp;
cmake -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=&kde-dir; \
      -DKDE_DEFAULT_HOME=.kde4 \
      -DSYSCONF_INSTALL_DIR=/etc/kde4 \
      .. &amp;&amp;
make</userinput></screen>

    <para>Maintenant, en tant qu'utilisateur <systemitem class="username">root</systemitem>&nbsp;:</para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>make install</userinput></screen>

  </sect2>

  <sect2 role="commands">
    <title>Explications des commandes</title>

 <para><option>patch -Np1 -i ../kde-runt...</option>&nbsp;: Ce correctif corrige
 l'édition de liens vers <application>libtirpc</application>.</para>

  </sect2>

